DMAXUK.uk.description: A concerning weigh-in forces Paul on a 1400km trek for new mining equipment. In the remote Pilbara region, mechanical issues cause tensions for the Ferals. S8, Ep11

DMAXUK.uk.title: Aussie Gold Hunters
DMAXUK.uk.description: A series of setbacks threaten to ruin the Gold Devils' recovery plants. Plus, the Ferals suffer a serious gold drought on Kim North's Mount Shovel lease. S8, Ep13

DMAXUK.uk.description: Miami. The buyers are at Miami International Airport, home to 10,000 lost bags every year. Mark bids on bags of jewellery hoping to strike gold and Billy eyes up a heavy bag. S1, Ep1

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: London. Auction specialists fly across the Atlantic to bid on lost bags in London. Sally convinces Laurence to bid big and Mark and Billy compete to win interesting luggage. S1, Ep2

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Indianapolis. The buyers are in Indianapolis to bid on bags, antiques and sports memorabilia. The Martins argue over a vintage music player and Mark spots a rare boxing collectable. S1, Ep3

DMAXUK.uk.title: Baggage Battles
DMAXUK.uk.description: Atlanta. The buyers are in Atlanta to bid on items at an unclaimed freight auction. Billy and Mark are interested in military items and the Martins discover an unusual find! S1, Ep4

DMAXUK.uk.description: New Jersey. The buyers bid on lucrative cargo at the US customs auction in New Jersey. Here, Mark takes a gamble while Billy and the Martins spot vintage bicycles. S1, Ep5

DMAXUK.uk.description: Los Angeles. Buyers bid on seized items and property at a police auction in Los Angeles. Billy and the Martins compete to win antique weapons, and Mark gambles on gold. S1, Ep6

DMAXUK.uk.description: Scotland. The buyers bid on lost property at a police auction in Glasgow, Scotland. The Martins and Billy compete to win vintage military snuff mull and Mark looks at farm tools. S1, Ep7

DMAXUK.uk.description: Florida. The buyers are in Florida at the largest airport auction in the world. Laurence and Sally and Billy compete for a unique bronze statue while Mark bids on archery equipment. S1, Ep8

DMAXUK.uk.title: Junkyard Empire

DMAXUK.uk.title: Junkyard Empire

DMAXUK.uk.description: Just A Couple Heres And Theres. A 1964 Corvette arrives at the shop for a simple repaint. But the job quickly turns into much more with new wheels and a whole new interior. S7, Ep11

DMAXUK.uk.description: That's Never Been Done. Dave convinces the client to make the '67 C10 truck into a convertible. Plus, Kevin takes on a new personal project with a Cadillac Escalade. S7, Ep13
